[1.1.0] - 2026-02-25
Added
Dual-Theme Support: Comprehensive Light and Dark mode styling using CSS-in-JS logic.
Testimonials: Automatic rotating UI for client feedback.
Interactive Booking: Fully functional Formspree integration with AJAX submission and error handling.

Fixed
Resolved framer-motion calculation error by enforcing relative positioning on the main container.
Fixed 403 Forbidden API errors by updating CORS headers and AJAX settings.
Corrected background color "ghosting" during scroll transitions.

Current Version: 1.1.0

Previous Versions:
v1.1.0 (Current): Implemented theme-aware UI logic. Added dynamic scroll-based background transitions (Light/Dark mode) and integrated Formspree AJAX booking with custom success states.
v1.0.5: General Bug Fixes.
v1.0.0 (The Cinematic Update): Complete home page overhaul featuring high-end cinematic transitions and a curated visual experience.
v0.8.0: Email configuration updates and layout bug fixes.
v0.5.0: Massive website overhaul and initial implementation of auto-dark mode logic.
v0.1.0: Initial build and deployment.
